my toes, making them pink again. Loose moon dust falling to the bare wooden floor makes me think of fairy dust and magical powders.  Am I even awake?  Momma always taught me that I should always organize myself before heading to bed. Always examine your backpacks after long trips and hunting expeditions in case a critter gets into your food supply. So I empty my bags on top of my bed and sift through the papers, runes, coin, and other odd treasures. My fingers trace a couple of old letters and pictures.<br><br> I still carry his picture. Why can't I just get over him? Leaning my head back against the bedpost, I start to go into a deep gaze.  <br><br> I got &quot;my official letter&quot; exactly 17 days ago. <br><br> To be honest, I really expected it. <br><br> War is harsh. Why is there so much hate when there is plenty of loving to be had?  That's why I went to Firona Vie, where we placed our marriage papers in a join vault.  I went to the registrar responsible for surnames and put in an application to change my name.  <br><br> &quot;Hopeful Warsong. That's me&quot;<br> <br> &quot;Maughan Warsong. Deceased.&quot;<br><br> When I had to explain that to this lady, I felt so numb. Like part of me was laying cold, face down in the snow off the cliff in Cobalt Scar, where they had found him...<br><br> &quot;My profession, ma'am?&quot; &quot;Oh, sorry I forgot to fill in that spot...&quot;<br><br>  What's the point, I thought.<br><br> &quot;Musician&quot; I told her. &quot;I'm actually just passing through Kunark, I'm on tour.&quot;<br><br>  Touring for what? Him? He's dead, Hope. Get over it.<br><br>  <br>Crickets chirp below in the thicket under my treetop getaway.  My agent stops in to give me my tour agenda for the next month. It's going to be a long summer I can see. Many many trips in Velious and Luclin... God, not Velious...<br><br>  Tell me there's something more out there for me. <br><br>  For now, I'm Hopeful Lovesong.  Pouring my heart out through song to everyone who could use it.  Love songs. Heh. Can I get some of that? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br> <p><center><img src= http://www.lvcm.com/guild/hope/summerofhope2.jpg></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uhopefulwarsong.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hopeful Warsong</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.naturallynovascotia.com/images/noteicon.gif" BORDER=0> at: 7/21/02 2:44:05 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uuhrlik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Uhrlik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#333333>(8/12/02 7:37:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstavernfrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=112.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Goodbye &quot;War Songs&quot;,  Hello &quot;Summer of Ho</span><hr size=1> Gotta say, Hopeful, you're an amazing writer. I get engrossed in the heartache of the poor bard, searching in vain for her lost love. Please keep writing. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Uhrlik Mystblade<BR>Officer, Guild Ambassador<BR>and Championof Feir'Dal<P><I>"May you die with Honor and Purpose"</I></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstavernfrm22.showPrevMessage?topicID=112.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstavernfrm22.showNextMessage?topicID=112.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstavernfrm22.show